Reasoning: The paper discusses a logic that encodes probabilistic temporal logic and provides a model-checking algorithm for computing the denotational value of a formula in a probabilistic transition system. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
